{{nihongo|'''Sakura Japanese Language School'''|lead=yes|さくら日本語学校|Sakura Nihongo Gakkō}} is a school in [[District 3, Ho Chi Minh City|District 3]], [[Ho Chi Minh City]], [[Vietnam]]. This is one of two schools that specializing in teaching [[Japanese language]] in this city, the other being [[Dong Du Japanese language School]]. Many of its teachers come from [[Japan]]. The learning program and coursebooks as well as language skill classification here are in strict accordance with the norms set forth by the [[Japanese education system]]. Most of [[undergraduate]]s in this city and in surrounding [[Provinces of Vietnam|provinces]] take a language course here before joining Japanese universities.

